Troubleshooting Tips
Database locked error:

Ensure only one application instance is running
Delete job_history.db and restart
Import errors:

Verify virtual environment is activated
Reinstall dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
Tests fail with 404:

Check that routes are registered in app/__init__.py
Verify blueprint is imported correctly
Filter returns no results:

Check query parameter names match exactly
Verify sample data exists in database
